  "description": "Computes the cumulative sum of input tensor along axis.",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "Parameters",
      "description": "exclusive(bool,optional) – By default, this op performs an inclusive cumsum, which means that the first\nelement of the input is identical to the first element of the output. Default:False.reverse(bool,optional) – IfTrue, perform inverse cumulative sum. Default:False."
